These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, swimming, weightlifting, ice-hockey, climbing
5 different games are played: domino, chess, billiard, mah-jongg, backgammon
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing billiard##2
6. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Sport          | swimming | basketball | climbing | ice-hockey | weightlifting |
| Game   | billiard  | backgammon      | mah-jongg   | domino     | chess    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, police-officer, engineer, writer, freelancer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, comedy, drama, martial-arts, adventure
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the freelancer is in the middle##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
5. the person watching disaster movies is between the engineer and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the manager##1
7. the engineer is on the left of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Job   | engineer     | writer       | freelancer    | manager | police-officer   |
| Movie-Genre      | comedy | disaster | martial-arts | adventure      | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, spanish, french, japanese, canadian
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, july, may, june, december
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the chinese##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
7. the french is on the right of the chinese##1
8. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Nationality         | chinese | french | spanish | japanese    | canadian |
| Birthday   | june     | march        | may      | july | december      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, photographer, mechanic, librarian, journalist
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, taxi, jet-ski, tram, snowmobile
1. the mechanic is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
4. the journalist is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the mechanic is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the photographer is between the person driving the jet-ski and the journalist##2
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Job         | manager      | librarian | mechanic | photographer   | journalist  |
| Transport   | tram | snowmobile    | jet-ski        | trike | taxi |

