.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, november, december, february, april
City: miami, hannover, berlin, nizza, new-york
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Birthday      | april      | november | october   | february  | december  |
| City   | berlin | nizza | miami | hannover | new-york |

