.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking, photography, reading
5 different games are played: billiard, poker, bridge, domino, backgammon
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
2. the person playing poker is between the person playing backgammon and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Hobby   | puzzles        | card-games                | photography  | woodworking  | reading            |
| Game        | billiard | backgammon | poker | bridge | domino |

