.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, italian, canadian, british, indonesian
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, techno, funk, rock, soul
1. the british is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
2. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
3. the italian is in the middle##1
4. the british is on the left of the indian##1
5. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4
6. the indian is on the far right##1
7. the fan of house is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
8. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of techno##1
9. the fan of rock is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Nationality   | indonesian       | canadian   | italian    | british    | indian |
| Music-Genre        | funk | house | techno | soul | rock     |

