.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, blend, fonseca, game, bluemaster
5 different pets are kept: cat, fish, ferret, chinchilla, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the ferret is the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the game-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Cigar      | fonseca  | bolivar       | blend      | game  | bluemaster   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | cat | chinchilla | fish | ferret |

