.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, blues, d&b, house, classical
The people have 5 different jobs:  librarian, writer, dancer, lawyer, journalist
1. the librarian is in an even position##4
2. the fan of house is the lawyer##1
3. the lawyer is the fan of house##1
4. the fan of house is on the far right##1
5. the fan of blues is the librarian##1
6. the fan of d&b is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
7. the journalist is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
8. the writer is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | classical | blues | d&b     | reggae | house |
| Job           | writer | librarian     | dancer | journalist    | lawyer      |

