.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-10::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, fanta, almond-milk, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: r&b, classical, jazz, reggae, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of classical is the person drinking tea##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Beverage     | water | fanta | almond-milk | tea | juice |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | salsa | reggae    | classical    | r&b  |

