.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann, montecristo, bongani, davidoff
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, water, fanta, hot-chocolate, milk
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the aristoff-smoker is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking water##2
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking milk is the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
7. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Cigar    | dannemann    | davidoff  | aristoff      | bongani     | montecristo |
| Beverage   | juice | water | hot-chocolate | fanta | milk |

