.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
5 different games are played: chess, monopoly, billiard, backgammon, scrabble
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, mystery, horror
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the person playing chess##1
3. the person watching horror movies is in the middle##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person playing monopoly##2
7. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Game        | backgammon | scrabble | chess  | billiard | monopoly     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | romance     | horror | adventure      | mystery |

