.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, october, december, february, march
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, zombie, crime, animation, documentary
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's birthday is in december##2
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
8. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Birthday      | march       | december | october | february   | june   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | zombie | documentary  | horror | crime |

