.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, golf, sailing, cricket, soccer
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, scientist, police-officer, teacher, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
4. the police-officer is on the left of the dressmaker##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
6. the teacher is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
7. the teacher is between the scientist and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Sport    | soccer   | cricket  | golf     | lacrosse | sailing |
| Job   | manager | police-officer | dressmaker | teacher | scientist      |

