.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, artichoke, spinach, orange, peach
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia, begonia, bellflower, poppy
1. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
6. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
7. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
8. the person who growsbellflower is in the middle##1
9. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Food   | artichoke  | spinach    | orange | asparagus   | peach |
| Flower   | poppy | dahlia | bellflower    | rose | begonia |

