5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff, bluemaster, swisher, cain
1. the indonesian is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the mexican is on the far right##1
4. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the nigerian is on the left or right of the australian##3
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Nationality           | nigerian | australian | french | indonesian | mexican   |
| Cigar   | davidoff       | bluemaster            | oliveros    | swisher     | cain |

