.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, miami, new-york, prague
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, july, august, october, march
1. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| City   | hannover | new-york | miami     | prague     | san-francisco |
| Birthday     | october   | july   | november | august | march  |

