.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
There 5 different types of food: peas, grapes, papaya, asparagus, kale
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, bellflower, iris, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
5. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
8. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
9. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Food   | peas | grapes | kale     | papaya | asparagus |
| Flower     | iris       | orchid   | bellflower | dahlia   | marigold        |

