.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, snowmobile, car, skateboard
The people have 5 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, coach, writer, chef
1. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
2. the coach is the coach##1
3. the writer is on the far left##1
4. the engineer is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
5. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the motorbike and the chef##2
6. the lawyer is between the person driving the car and the chef##2
7. the writer is in an odd position##4
8. the chef is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Transport         | car | snowmobile | tram | skateboard | motorbike     |
| Job   | writer    | lawyer   | chef       | coach | engineer |

