.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, freelancer, manager, designer, coach
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, february, april, january, december
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the coach##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the coach##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in january##2
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the coach##1
5. the designer is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the dressmaker##1
7. the freelancer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Job   | dressmaker | manager      | designer | coach     | freelancer      |
| Birthday     | december | february | january | may | april |

 